SetBonus: {
	FlinxHood: Increese max minions by 1
	AcidCobwebHood:
		'''
		Reduse mana cost by 5% 
		Increese mana regen a bit
		Increese max mana by 60;
		Increese magic damage by 5%
		On you got hit by npc you shoot with web
		You dont need to get damage if youre hp lower then 25%
		'''
	AcidCobwebMask:
		'''
		Increese max minions and turrets by 1 
		Increese summoner damage by 5%
		On you got hit by npc you shoot with web
		You dont need to get damage if youre hp lower then 25%
		'''
	GranithShellHelmet:
		'''
		Increese melee damage by 5%
		Scorspider sting protects you
		'''
	GranithShellMask:
		'''
		Increese ranged damage by 5%
		You shoot with Scorspider projectiles
		'''
	StarPowerSet: На противников которых вы ранили с неба падают звезды
}

